reviews.text:
Very nice place, I have been their new location at Burnaby;
When I came in, a lady with her kind smile brought me into a meeting room;  After 5 mins, Mr. Cui meet me and introduce the real estate information in Vancouver;  I have seen his face everywhere, and I could not believe that the real superstar was sitting with me!
One week later, he came to my house and showed me more about my house;  Even though I did not sell my house at that time, I will ask him to list my house when I moved to other area.

Very knowledgeable on house construction;
Excellent service house sales and buying;
Exceed my expectations on sales of my house;
Effectively collaborates with client and shows ability to come with new solutions when there is an issue.
I would definitely like to work with these team members again in the future.
